            },
            "description": "The competition called for projects to create an installation in one of the empty spaces at the Gallery of Merchants, in the center of Athens, and organize concepts that will emerge out of open, participatory workshops for the exhibition \"traces of commerce\" that would take place in Athens in the Gallery of Merchants, Voulis Street 9. The City of Athens, through the operational program of the Athens Development and Destination Management Agency \u00abProject Athens\u00bb, and with the support of its citizens\u2019 networking platform \u00abSyn Athina\u00bb, launched this program of urban interventions in the spatial context and the commercial activity of Athens. The goal of the program was to project misused spaces of the city center offering at the same time space for experimentation to young creative practitioners and multidisciplinary collectives to question and provoke the future of the migrating industries and the disappearance of the old trade and craftsmanship.\n ",
